        "Title": "No More Missed Calls",
        "Location": "LOCATION_GOLDEN_GECKO",
        "PublicId": "127488459744",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/golden/mission_gecko/scene_gecko_basic.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 64102a8d-0f3c-40cb-8ad1-3b2943be98bd).Image",
        "Description": "Good Day 47,\rLove is in the air and so is corporate negligence. A maintenance staff member and a security guard, too busy whispering sweet nothings over their phones, have let the building’s security and maintenance fall apart. Their constant distractions have led to costly mishaps and management has had enough.They now want them offline, literally.\rSo you have to take care of it and make sure their last call gets dropped permanently.\r\rGood Luck.\r\rBy - SW\r\r(Note - ICA Explosive Phone - Unlocked by reaching Mastery level 18 on Bangkok)\r\n\r\n<HCCE>",
